QuestData.Title: An Embarrassing Incident
QuestData.Description: There's one little problem we have to solve before we head out. You see, I can't seem to find the keys to my flying machine.$B$BI've looked pretty much everywhere for them... maybe you can give me a hand. Only place I haven't looked yet is inside the lake.$B$BI'll even give you my very own air tank. It's almost empty, but it's got a couple of hits left.
QuestData.LogDescription: Look for Vic's Keys inside the lake at River's Heart.
